dbt_version.comment: Installed version of dbt that is currently running.

project_name.name: project_name
project_name.comment: Name for the root-level project which is being run by dbt.

run_started_at.comment: The start timestamp of the dbt execution which generated the record.

full_refresh_flag.name: full_refresh_flag
full_refresh_flag.comment: Boolean flag indicating whether the dbt run was in full refresh mode or not.

target_profile_name.comment: The name of the active profile.

target_name.comment: The name of the active target.

target_schema.comment: The name of the target dbt schema.

target_threads.name: target_threads
target_threads.comment: The number of threads in use by dbt.

dbt_cloud_job_id.name: dbt_cloud_job_id

dbt_cloud_run_id.name: dbt_cloud_run_id
dbt_cloud_run_id.comment: The ID of this particular run.

dbt_cloud_run_reason_category.comment: The "category" of the trigger for this run.

dbt_cloud_run_reason.comment: The specific trigger for this run.

invocation_args.name: invocation_args
